{"tid":1037281,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【好看不好用】當用全球最貴的 Mate X 玩「王者榮耀」立即哭出來！","createTime":"2019-02-25T22:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T08:58:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":143,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6ff1ac2f12c12968214957a041ac9c8058b6f2","tid":1037281,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T22:54:32.000Z","msg":"Feb 25, 2019<br />\n摺疊式手機華為 Mate X 發佈後，人們仍然充滿疑問，而「華為終情局」在抖音分享了用 Mate X 玩《王者榮耀》的情況。當用戶在 6.6 吋螢幕玩遊戲時，分別跟現時不太大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xrTod1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xrTod1.png&h=f3d27156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，當使用大螢幕時，問題就來了！首先華為的螢幕解像度為 2480X2200，其實就是比較接近一個正方形，Mate X 竟然將中間部份裁出來放大，但可視的範圍卻變得少很多，對真正的玩家實在很沒趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/26/065334_0742a7d8c0ee0d9c32c71248dac86863.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F26%2F065334_0742a7d8c0ee0d9c32c71248dac86863.png&h=f221feba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信，除了玩遊戲會出問題，甚至看 Youtube、看 Netflix 也會有類似的情況出現。這是螢幕比例的限制，如果不用「黑邊」來填補，就要裁掉部份空間才行。相對 Samsung Galaxy Fold 螢幕的 4.2:3（較接近 iPad mini 的 4:3)，華為的 Mate X 顯示比例的確帶來一些相容性的疑問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UKoqqh4puaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUKoqqh4puaA&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=44b955b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UKoqqh4puaA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/02/25/matex-play-game-video/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F02%2F25%2Fmatex-play-game-video%2F&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=370f31be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/02/25/matex-play-game-video/</a>"},{"pid":"be6d7b97e83f0f2038fa59b415fba3c89a793792","tid":1037281,"uid":12628,"like":219,"dislike":5,"score":214,"citedBy":0,"replyT